A **pension income calculator** tells you the sustainable monthly withdrawal from your retirement corpus. If your corpus earns 7–8% post-retirement and you withdraw 5–6% annually, the corpus can last 25–35 years. This calculator helps you find the right balance between withdrawal amount, corpus depletion timeline, and leaving a residual estate.
